    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Support? From who? Everyone saw me as this authority, this pioneer. Now when they look at me, they just see a fraud. I can't go back to the lab, I can't face my peers, and there is no \"journey\" worth continuing when the destination was a delusion. It feels like the only honest thing left to do is just... stop. To just cease existing so the lie doesn't keep going.",
